1.0.name: wordpress/pinpress
1.0.description: A responsive theme with neat column layout similar to pinterest. If you need a perfect mobile theme, then pinpress might be the right option. combine the plugin Gamma gallery - http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/gamma-gallery/ to see amazing effects.
